snippet.title: Finally !! We Create Black Hole Using Water | Part-2
snippet.description:
No VFX Everything Is REAL Which You Will See In This Video.

Watch Making Process - We Build Black Hole Making Machine -100% Real | Part-1 - https://youtu.be/91pe_U35C6U

Our Black Hole Making Machine use 40000 Liters Of Water To Operate.

Yes I Know This Is Not Real Black Hole Obviously, But Our Black Hole Also Has Some Similar Properties Which Real Black Hole Has Like Gravity, Accretion Disks etc.

A black hole is a region of spacetime where gravity is so strong that nothing, including light or other electromagnetic waves has enough energy to escape its event horizon. 

Our blackhole have also powerful gravity in the center and can pull a human size object inside the center.

If We Throw Any Object In The Machine They Start Orbiting The Black Hole Like The Galaxies, Stars Or Any Matter Orbit Real The Black Hole. And At The End Our Black Hole Can Also Sucks Everything That Comes On It's Way.

Love You All.

snippet.title: India's Republic Day Parade 26th January, 2023 - LIVE
snippet.description:
#RepublicDay Parade 2023 का सीधा प्रसारण | 26 January Parade Live #RepublicDayparade #RepublicDay2023 #IndiaRepublicDay #गणतंत्रदिवस India celebrates her 74th Republic Day on 26 January 2023. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 74th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan. 

#IndianRepublicDay2023 #RepublicDayFullParade #IndianArmy #IndiacelebratesRepublicDay #RepublicDaycelebrations #IndianNationalFlag #GantantraDivasParade #HappyRepublicDay #RepublicDay2023 #74thRepublicDay #RepublicDayParade2023 #EgyptPresident Abdel Fattah al-Sisi  #DroupadiMurmu

snippet.title: Dr. Vikas Divyakirti Sir क्यों बोले '1 भी बात गलत हुई तो मैं ज़िम्मेदार हूं' 🤔 | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Vikas जी की तरह अपने Skills, मेहनत, ज़िद और जुनून के दम पर बनें Successful :https://joshskills.app.link/4iaNjbgiVwb

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti’s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 01 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. Why Vikas Sir's surname is Dvyakirti?
2. What was his UPSC Exam Result?
3. How Dr. Vikas Divyakirti handles Drishti IAS and what is his role?
4. What is Dr. Vikas Divyakirti's ideology regarding Anxiety and Depression?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. Many people put Dr. Vikas Divyakirti ji's Motivational Shorts and Videos on their Status. He also has a YouTube channel named Vikas Divyakirti. 

By watching this Motivational Speech of Dr.Vikas Divyakirti, we will get the guidance and courage to become successful.

जोश Talks लाया है एक ऐसी सिरीज़ जिसमें हम जानेंगे Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Professional और Personal Lifestyle के बारे में. साथ ही जानेंगे कि इनके UPSC Exam Preparation को लेकर क्या विचार हैं और इनकी क्या Life Inspirations रही हैं.

ये इस सिरीज़ का Episode 01 है जिसमें Dr. Vikas Divyakirti निम्नलिखित सवालों पर चर्चा करेंगे -

1. Vikas Sir का Surname Dvyakirti ही क्यों पड़ा?
2. इनका UPSC Exam Result क्या था?
3. Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी Drishti IAS कैसे संभालते हैं? 
4. Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी के  Anxiety और Depression को लेकर क्या विचार हैं?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी IAS Trainer, Author और lecturer हैं. Drishti IAS Coaching Classes जो कि Delhi में एक UPSC Coaching Institute है, ये उसके Founder हैं. इनका जन्म Haryana में हुआ. इन्होंने Delhi University से Hindi literature में MA किया है. हुमनें इनको Drishti IAS पर UPSC Mock Interview लेते हुए सुना होगा. बच्चे से लेकर बूढ़े तक इनकी बातों के Fan हैं. कईं लोग Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Motivational Shorts और Videos अपने Status पर लागते हैं. इनका एक YouTube channel भी है जिसका नाम है Vikas Divyakirti. 

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की ये Motivational Speech देख कर हमें Successful बनने का मार्गदर्शन और हौसला मिलेगा. 

#JoshTalksHindi #DrVikasDivyakirtiJoshTalks #DrVikasDivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtisir #vikasdivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtimotivation #vikasdivyakirtibiography #drvikasdivyakirti #drvikasdivyakirtisir #drvikasdivyakirtiinterview #drvikasdivyakirtimotivation #drvikasdivyakirtimotivational

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi...

We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 74th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 10 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Fazila Qazi as Aneela

Haris Waheed

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 09 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 09 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 25th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

My melancholia

snippet.title: शज़ैम! फ्युरी ऑफ द गॉड्स (Shazam! Fury Of The Gods) - Official Hindi Trailer 2
snippet.description:
वक़्त आ गया है ज़िम्मेदारियाँ उठाने का। देखिये 'शज़ैम! फ्युरी ऑफ द गॉड्स' का नया हिंदी ट्रेलर। #ShazamMovie in English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu 17 मार्च से सिनेमाघरों में।

Website: www.warnerbros-india.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WarnerBrosIndia
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/warnerbrosindia
Twitter: https://twitter.com/warnerbrosindia

SHAZAM! FURY OF THE GODS 
From New Line Cinema comes “Shazam! Fury of the Gods,” which continues the story of teenage Billy Batson who, upon reciting the magic word “SHAZAM!,” is transformed into his adult Super Hero alter ego, Shazam. “Shazam! Fury of the Gods” stars returning cast members Zachary Levi (“Thor: Ragnarok”) as Shazam; Asher Angel (“Andi Mack”) as Billy Batson; Jack Dylan Grazer (“It Chapter Two”) as Freddy Freeman; Adam Brody (“Promising Young Woman”) as Super Hero Freddy; Ross Butler (“Raya and the Last Dragon”) as Super Hero Eugene; Meagan Good (“Day Shift”) as Super Hero Darla; D.J. Cotrona (“G.I. Joe: Retaliation”) as Super Hero Pedro; Grace Caroline Currey (“Annabelle: Creation”) as Mary Bromfield / Super Hero Mary; Faithe Herman (“This Is Us”) as Darla Dudley; Ian Chen (“A Dog’s Journey”) as Eugene Choi; Jovan Armand (“Second Chances”) as Pedro Pena; Marta Milans (“White Lines”) as Rosa Vasquez; Cooper Andrews (“The Walking Dead”) as Victor Vasquez; with Djimon Hounsou (“A Quiet Place Part II”) as Wizard.  Joining the cast are Rachel Zegler (“West Side Story”), with Lucy Liu (“Kung Fu Panda” franchise) and Helen Mirren (“F9: The Fast Saga”).  The film is directed by David F. Sandberg (“Shazam!,” “Annabelle: Creation”) and produced by Peter Safran (“Aquaman,” “The Suicide Squad”). It is written by Henry Gayden (“Shazam!,” “There’s Someone Inside Your House”) and Chris Morgan (“Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw,” “The Fate of the Furious”), based on characters from DC; Shazam! was created by Bill Parker and C.C. Beck. Executive producers are Walter Hamada, Adam Schlagman, Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Victoria Palmeri, Marcus Viscidi and Geoff Johns.  Joining director Sandberg behind-the-camera are director of photography Gyula Pados (the “Jumanji” franchise), production designer Paul Kirby (“The Old Guard,” “Jason Bourne”) and editor Michel Aller (“Shazam!,” “The Nun”). The music supervisor is Season Kent (“DC League of Super-Pets,” “The Addams Family 2”) and the music is by Christophe Beck (“Free Guy,” “Frozen II”). Visual effects supervisors are Bruce Jones (“Aquaman,” “It”) and Raymond Chen (“Alita: 
Battle Angel,” “The Meg”). The costume designer is Louise Mingenbach (“Jumanji: The Next Level,” “Godzilla: King of the Monsters”).  New Line Cinema presents A Peter Safran Production of A David F. Sandberg Film, “Shazam! Fury of the Gods,” which is set to open in cinemas in India beginning March 17, 2023.

#WarnerBrosIndia #ShazamHindiTrailer2

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 11 Teaser - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 11 Teaser - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Real Madrid 3-1 Atlético de Madrid | HIGHLIGHTS | Copa del Rey
snippet.description:
Real Madrid are in the semi-finals of the Copa del Rey after beating Atlético de Madrid (Real Madrid 3-1 Atlético de Madrid). Enjoy the highlights of a magical night at the Santiago Bernabéu. Carlo Ancelotti's team came from behind to win the derby after falling behind early at the Santiago Bernabéu and won the match in extra time. Álvaro Morata gave Atlético the lead in the first half before Rodrygo's equalizer in the second half caused an eruption of celebrations at the Bernabéu with a solo goal. Captain Karim Benzema then scored to make it 2-1 at the very end of the first period of extra time, before Vini Jr. added a goal of his own to make it 3-1 and seal the win.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3679 - 27 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3679: Taarak Phas Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha calls from behind, and Taarak turns around to respond, colliding with a passerby and falling into a mud puddle. As a result, his yellow shirt gets stained. Everyone rushes to Taarak's location. Fortunately, he is not injured, but his shirt is ruined. Taarak blames Jetha for the mishap, but the Gokuldham ladies back him up, claiming that he didn't do it on purpose. Taarak will now wear a green shirt because he was unable to obtain another yellow shirt. Champaklal arrives on the scene and decides to support Taarak in front of his boss. Stay tuned to find out how Champaklal saves Taarak from a reprimand from his boss.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3679, 27 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000207391

snippet.title: Aye Watan Tere Liye - Lyrical | Karma | Mohammad Aziz, Kavita Krishnamurthy | Patriotic Songs
snippet.description:
Watch the special patriotic Song " Aye Watan Tere Liye" From Karma Movie Sung By Mohammad Aziz, Kavita Krishnamurthy @tipsofficial 

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official, Subscribe on the below link.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

Song Details :
Star Cast: Dilip Kumar, Nutan, Naseeruddin Shah, Jackie Shroff, Anil Kapoor, Anupam Kher, Sridevi, Poonam Dhillon
Singers: Mohammad Aziz, Kavita Krishnamurthy
Music Director:  Laxmikant Pyarelal
Lyrics by: Anand Bakshi
Producer & Director: Subhash Ghai

Lyrics:
Mera Karma Tu Mera Dharma Tu 
Tera Sab Kuch Main Mera Sab Kuch Tu
Har Karam Apna Karenge
Har Karam Apna Karenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Har Karam Apna Karenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Har Karam Apna Karenge Aye Watan Tere Liye


Tu Mera Karma Tu Mera Dharma Tu Mera Abhiman Hai
Aye Watan Mehboob Mere Tujhpe Dil Kurban Hai
Aye Watan Mehboob Mere Tujhpe Dil Kurban Hai
Hum Jiyenge Aur Marenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye

Hindu Muslim Sikh Isayi Hum Watan Hum Naam Hai
Hindu Muslim Sikh Isayi Hum Watan Hum Naam Hai
Jo Kare Inko Juda Mazhab Nahi Ilzam Hai
Hum Jiyenge Aur Marenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye

Teri Galiyon Mein Chala Kar Nafraton Ki Goliya
Loot Te Hai Kuch Lutere Dulhano Ki Doliyan
Loot Rahe Hai Aap Woh Apne Gharon Ko Loot Kar
Khelte Hai Bekhabar Apne Lahu Se Holiya
Hum Jiyenge Aur Marenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye

#republicday #patrioticsong #ayewatan #hindisongs #deshbhakti #deshbhaktisong #deshbhaktistatus #ganatantradivas

snippet.title: Republic Day 2023 |  Highlights Of The Republic Day Parade 2023 | 26th January 2023 Parade | News18
snippet.description:
Republic Day 2023 |  Highlights Of The Republic Day Parade 2023 | 26th January 2023 Parade | News18 

The 74th Republic Day Parade was about the spectacular display of made-in-India weapons, increased role of 'Nari Shakti' in the Armed Forces and signs of the country leaving behind its colonial past. For the first time in the history of India’s Republic Day, the British-era 25-pounder guns, which had been used for decades for the 21-gun salute, were replaced with the indigenous 105mm Indian Field Guns. The vintage artillery, which was once used in the World War II, fell silent and the desi guns boomed for the ceremonial gun salute. Lt Commander Disha Amrith, 29, was the first Navy woman officer to lead a naval contingent of 144 sailors, showcasing the increasing role of 'Nari Shakti' in the military. Armed with assault rifles, women soldiers in colourful uniforms, usually deployed along the desert border with Pakistan, were for the first time joined the BSF camel contingent. Women officers were also part of the contingents of Corps of Signals, Army Air Defence and Army Daredevils

*About* 
------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.

snippet.title: Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Episode 34 | Turkish Drama| Urdu Dubbing | Sen Cal Kapimi | 27th Jan 2023 |
snippet.description:
Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Sen Cal Kapimi | You knock on my Door |


#Urdu1 #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed #sencalkapimi #sençalkapımı #DastakMayrayDilPay #sençalkapımı #sencalkapimi #youknockonmydoor #handeercel #handeerçel #kerembürsin #karembursin #melisadöngel #bigeönal #loveisintheair #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.


Produced by: MF YAPIM
Licensor: MADD Entertainment

snippet.title: शुभ बसंत पंचमी स्पेशल - सरस्वती माता यह चमत्कारी कथा सुनने से ज्ञान, बुद्धि और धन समृद्धि आती है
snippet.description:
Basant Panchami 2023 : 
हिंदू धर्म में बसंत पंचमी का विशेष खास महत्व होता है. बसंत पंचमी हर साल माघ माह के शुक्ल पक्ष की पंचमी तिथि के दिन मनाई जाती है. बसंत पंचमी के दिन बड़े ही धूमधाम से मां सरस्वती की पूजा की जाती है. इस साल बसंत पंचमी का पर्व 26 जनवरी 2023 के दिन गुरुवार को मनाया जाएगा. मान्यता है कि विद्यार्थियों के लिए बसंत पंचमी का खास महत्व है. बसंत पंचमी के दिन विद्या और ज्ञान की देवी मां सरस्वती के पूजा करने से विशेष लाभ मिलता है

#ShreePanchami

Twitter - emiwaytweets
Facebook - emiway37

Merch
Official EB store :- https://www.bantai.in/product-category/merchandise/


(LYRICS ENGLISH TRANSLATIONS)

(Hook)

What’s up company (gang)
We Earning lotta money  
They think they are wise 
But they are too funny 
Don’t act like a bit*h 
We are they street OG’s
We know people from 
37,70 till 17 (Hood Pincodes in Mumbai)

(Verse 1)

Stop popping pills  
What’s up dawg are you different
Or should i teach you how to be 
Go anywhere but don’t f**k around here 
You wanna live in this country peacefully right ?
Or should i get your passport visa done 
Be aware 
Everyone is in thoughts 
How should i reach till Emiway Bantai 
We were Light in the Dark 
We ate from our  own plate
Didn’t steal from others plate 

Where are you ? 
Look here 
All my boys are roaming around 
Fearless 
One look all it takes to scare yall 
What do you want just tell me homie ? 

If your respect is important to you then 
Make sure you respect others too 
Or else will curse  you soo much that 
You will live your whole 
Life in fear 

Represting India 
One fight down 
Two fight straight to the grave 


(Verse 2)

(Mumbai slangs)
Its not lakhs its crore we talk 
Love is betrayal 
Soo make sure you 
Put you heart in right place 
You got one more chance 

If you fight  for yourself then world will say are wrong 
Either your sleep will be fulfilled or your dreams 

I’m speaking facts 
Who is supporting poor people 
There are no less rents anymore 
Weak people don’t have guts to change 
Their life 
We made it on our own 
That’s why we live life without worrying 

(Verse 3)

They are soft from inside 
But they act like tough outside 
Everyone is an artist 
No one is less than a criminal 
On the streets 
We changed to a good human 
Now we cruising with our parents 
We not scared of any tools or weapons 
We are only scared of god 

Leave this worldliness and go and hustle 
We are good human now but if it comes on us 
Then you better understand what will come to you 
My hood kid are more smarter than you 
Mom told work hard don’t choose wrong path 

If you don’t understand then just leave it 
Labels asking me for songs 
I gave them and took lot’s of money 
Now we gonna kill it with labels soon 

Knock knock on my doors 
Money coming faster 
Keep trying homie 
Don’t give up 
If you hustle today 
Tomorrow will be fun 
You will be successful 
Just keep going 

(Hook)

snippet.title: Thapki ने दी Shraddha को चेतावनी | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 605
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Thapki finds out that Shraddha was the mastermind behind the attack on Bihaan. Thapki warns Shraddha and asks her to stay away from Bihaan or face dire consequences. Will Shraddha pay heed to Thapki's threats?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Title: Saraswati Chalisa Fast
Singer: Anuradha Paudwal
Music Director: Navin-Manish
Edit & Gfx : Chetan Garud Productions LLP
Music Label: Music Nova

Lyrics:
जनक जननि पद्मरज
Janak Janani Padam Raj
निज मस्तक पर धारी
Nij Mastak Par Dhaari
बन्दौं मातु सरस्वती
Bandau Maatu Saraswati
बुद्धि बल दे दातारि
Buddhi Bal De Daataari
पूर्ण जगत में व्याप्त तव
Purna Jagat Mein Vyapt Tav
महिमा अमित अनंतु
Mahima Amit Anantu
दुष्टजनों के पाप को
Dushtajano Ke Paap Ko
मातु तु ही अब हन्तु
Maatu Tuhi Ab Hantu

जय श्री सकल बुद्धि बलरासी
Jai Shri Sakal Buddhi Balarasi
जय सर्वज्ञ अमर अविनाशी
Jai Sarvagya Amar Avinashi
जय जय जय वीणाकर धारी
Jai Jai Jai Vinakar Dhari
करती सदा सुहंस सवारी
Karti Sada Suhans Sawari

रूप चतुर्भुज धारी माता
Roop Chaturbhuja Dhari Mata
सकल विश्व अन्दर विख्याता
Sakal Vishva Andar Vikhyata
जग में पाप बुद्धि जब होती
Jag Mein Paap Buddhi Jab Hoti
तब ही धर्म की फीकी ज्योति
Tabhi Dharm Ki Phiki Jyoti

तब ही मातु का निज अवतारा
Tabhi Maatu Ka Nij Avatara
पाप हीन करती महि तारी
Paap Heen Karti Mahi Taara
वाल्मीकिजी थे हत्यारे
Balmiki Ji The Hatyare
तव प्रसाद जानै संसारा
Tav Prasad Jane Sansara

रामचरित जो रचे बनाई
Ramcharit Jo Rache Banaai
आदि कवि पदवी को पाई
Aadi Kavi Padavi Ko Paai
कालिदास जो भये विख्याता
Kalidas Jo Bhaye Vikhyata
तेरी कृपा दृष्टि से माता
Teri Kripa Drishti Se Mata

तुलसी सूर आदि विद्वाना
Tulsi Sur Aadi Vidvana
भये और जो ज्ञानी नाना
Bhaye Aur Jo Gyani Nana
तिन्ह न और रहेउ अवलम्बा
Tinahi Na Aur Raheu Avalamba
केवल किरपा आपकी अम्बा
Keval Kirpa Aapki Amba

करहु कृपा सोइ मातु भवानी
Karahu Kripa Soi Matu Bhavani
दुखित दीन निज दासहि जानी
Dukhit Din Nij Dasahi Jani
पुत्र करहिं अपराध बहूता
Putra Karai Aparadh Bahuta
तेहि न धरई चित सुंदर माता
Tehi Na Dharai Chitt Sundar Mata

राखु लाज जननि अब मेरी
Rakhu Laaj Janani Ab Meri
विनय करउं भांति बहु तेरी
Vinay Karu Bhanti Bahu Teri
मैं अनाथ तेरी अवलंबा
Mein Anath Teri Avalamba
कृपा करउ जय जय जगदंबा
Kripa Karau Jai Jai Jagadamba

मधु कैटभ जो अति बलवाना
Madhu Kaitabh Jo Ati Balwana
बाहुयुद्ध विष्णु से ठाना
Bahuyuddh Vishnu Se Thana
समर हजार पाँच में घोरा
Samar Hajar Panch Mein Ghora
फिर भी मुख उनसे नहीं मोरा
Phir Bhi Mukh Unse Nahi Mora

मातु सहाय कीन्ह तेहि काला
Matu Sahay Kinhi Tehi Kaala
बुद्धि विपरीत भई खलहाला
Buddhi Viparit Bhai Khalahala
तेहि ते मृत्यु भई खल केरी
Tehi To Mrityu Bhai Khal Keri
पुरवहु मातु मनोरथ मेरी
Purvahu Matu Manorath Meri

चंड मुण्ड जो थे विख्याता
Chand Mund Jo They Vikhyata
क्षण महु संहारे उन तेहि माता
Kshan Mahu Sanhare Un Tehi Mata
रक्त बीज से समरथ पापी
Raktabij Se Samarth Paapi
सुरमुनि हदय धरा सब कापी
Surmuni Hriday Dhara Sab Kapi

काटेउ सिर जिमि कदली खम्बा
Kaateu Sir Jim Kadali Khamba
बारबार बिन वउं जगदंबा
Baar Baar Binavau Jagadamba
जगप्रसिद्ध जो शुंभ निशुंभा
Jag Prasidhdh Jo Shumbh Nishumbha
क्षण में बाँधे ताहि तू अम्बा
Kshan Mein Badhe Taahi Tu Amba

Bharat Matu Budhi Phereu Jaai
Ramachandra Banvas Karai
Ehi Vidhi Ravan Vadh Tu Kinha
Sur Narmuni Sabkahu Sukh Dinha

Ko Samarath Tav Yash Gun Gaana
Nigam Anadi Anant Bakhana
Vishnu Rudra Aajas Kahina Mari
Jinki Ho Tum Rakshakari

Rakt Dantika Aur Shatakshi
Naam Apar Hai Danav Bhakshi
Durgam Kaaj Dhara Kar Kinha
Durga Naam Sakal Jag Linha

Durg Aadi Harni Tu Mata
Kripa Karahu Jab Jab Sukhdata
Nrip Kopit Jo Maaran Chahei
Kaanan Mein Ghere Mrig Nahei

Sagar Madhya Pot Ke Bhanje
Ati Toofaan Nahi Kou Sange
Bhoot Pret Badha Ya Dukh Mein
Ho Daridra Athava Sankat Mein

Naam Jape Mangal Sab Hoi
Sanshay Isme Karai Na Koi
Putrahin Jo Aatur Bhai
Sabei Chhandi Pooje Ehi Mai

Karai Path Nij Yeh Chalisa
Hoye Putra Sundar Gun Isha
Dhupadik Naivaidya Chadhavei
Sankat Rahit Avashy Ho Jaavei

Bhakti Maatu Ki Karei Hamesha
Nikat Na Aavei Tahi Kalesha
Bandi Path Kare Shat Baara
Bandi Paash Door Ho Saara

Ramsagar Badhi Setu Bhawani
Kije Krupa Das Nij Jani
Mata Surya Kaanti Tav
Andhakar Mam Roop

Dooban Se Raksha Karahu
Paru Na Mein Bhav Koop
Bal Buddhi Vidya Dehu Mohi
Sunahu Saraswati Maatu
Ram Sagar Adham Ko
Aashray Tu Hi Dedatu

snippet.title: இது எனக்கு பயங்கரமான அனுபவம்😱| First Day in Mongolia | Tamil Trekker
snippet.description:
#tamiltrekker #mongolia #coldest 

Hey backpackers, get ready for my exciting Mongolia series. Here's my vlog for the first day, sharing my day-1 experience with -27 degrees Celsius. 

My new year's first international trip started in Mongolia, and you can't imagine the freezing weather that welcomed me! If you're looking for a pleasant season to visit Mongolia, I recommend visiting when it's less cold. 

Watch my latest travel vlog to learn about Mongolia's relationship with India, local travelling, and more.

********************

Please Subscribe Us & Share the Videos & Let others get informed about this channel 👉 http://bit.ly/TamilTrekker

​********************

Checkout Our Existing Tamil Travel Videos Playlist:

Uzbekistan - https://bit.ly/3lFHHBJ
Dubai - https://bit.ly/3xpe6i8
Thailand Vlog: http://bit.ly/ThailandTravelVlog
Malaysia Vlog: http://bit.ly/MalaysiaTravelVlogs
Hitchhiking Vlog: hhttp://bit.ly/HitchhikingTravelVlog
Pakistan Vlog: http://bit.ly/PakistanTravelVlog
Tamil Travel Vlog: http://bit.ly/TamilTravelVlog
Manali Vlog: http://bit.ly/ManaliTravelVlog
Kerala Vlog: http://bit.ly/KeralaTravelVlog
Darjeeling Vlog: http://bit.ly/DarjeelingTravelVlog
Meghalaya Vlog: http://bit.ly/MeghalayaTravelVlog
North East Vlog: http://bit.ly/NorthEastTravelVlog
Delhi Vlog: http://bit.ly/DelhiTravelVlog
Kodaikanal Vlog: http://bit.ly/KodaikanalTravelVlog
TentCampingVlog: http://bit.ly/2PnWiSa
Travel Tips: http://bit.ly/2JoNyaO
Budget Tour Plan: http://bit.ly/2pRrej0

​********************

நான் புவனி தரன், பேக் பேக்கர், ஹிட்சிகர், வோல்கர் & ட்ரெக்கர், உலகம் முழுவதும் பயணம் செய்து எனது அனுபவங்களை அனைவருடனும் பகிர்ந்து கொள்கிறேன்.

புதிய இடங்களைப் பார்ப்பது, வெவ்வேறு கலாச்சாரத்தை அனுபவிப்பது, மக்களைப் பற்றி அறிந்து கொள்வது, இந்த அழகான உலகத்தை தமிழ் ட்ரெக்கர் வழியாக உங்களுக்குக் காட்ட முயற்சிப்பேன்.

எனது இந்த பயணத்தில் அனைவரையும் வெளியே செல்லவும், ஆராயவும், அவர்கள் சந்திக்கும் ஒவ்வொரு சூழ்நிலையையும் சிறப்பாகப் பயன்படுத்தவும் ஊக்குவிப்பதாகும்.

I'm Bhuvani Dharan, Solo travel enthusiast, Backpacker, hitchhiker, vlogger & trekker who travels the world and shares my experiences with everyone.

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

With an emphasis on traveling these vlogs are meant to encourage everyone to go out, explore & make the most out of every situation they come across.

​********************

To check out our travel & backpacking budget gears:  https://www.amazon.in/shop/tamiltrekker

புதிய இடங்களைப் பார்ப்பது, வெவ்வேறு கலாச்சாரத்தை அனுபவிப்பது, மக்களைப் பற்றி அறிந்து கொள்வது, இந்த அழகான உலகத்தை தமிழ் ட்ரெக்கர் வழியாக உங்களுக்குக் காட்ட முயற்சிப்பேன்.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3678 - 26 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3678: Taarak Ka Luck
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak finally gets ready in Iyer's yellow shirt. Meanwhile, everyone from Gokuldham pays him a visit to wish him luck on his big day. Popatlal, out of concern, catches a random guy from a temple who was wearing a yellow shirt. He wanted to take the yellow shirt off the guy and give it to Taarak. Anjali feels gratified about being surrounded by such caring Gokuldham people. Taarak's boss video calls him to check on his yellow shirt. After such a conundrum, will everything fall into place? Will Taarak be able to attend the meeting in the yellow shirt? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3678, 26 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000207235

🔸 Lyrics of Bharat Ka Rehnewaala Hoon :

jab zero diya mere bharat ne
bharat ne mere bharat ne
duniya ko tab ginti aayi
taro ki bhashha bharat ne
duniya ko pahle sikhalayi
deta na dashmalav bharat to
yu chand pe jana mushkil tha
dharti aur chand ki duri ka
andaza lagana mushkil tha

sabhyta jaha pahle aayi
sabhyta jaha pahle aayi
pahle janami hai jaha pe kalaa
apna bharat vo bharat hai
jiske pichhe sansar chala
sansar chala aur aage badha
yu aage badha, badhta hi gaya
bhagvan kare ye aur badhe
badhta hi rahe aur phule-phale
badhta hi rahe aur phule-phale

hai prit jaha ki rit sada, hai prit jaha ki rit sada
hai prit jaha ki rit sada, main geet waha ke gata hu
bharat ka rahne wala hu, bharat kie baat sunata hu
hai prit jaha ki rit sada

kale gore ka bhed nahi, har dil se hamara nata hai
kuch aur na aata ho hamko, hame pyar nibhana aata hai
jise maan chuki sari duniya, ho jise maan chuki sari duniya
main baat, main baat wahi dohrata hu
bharat ka rahne wala hu, bharat kie baat sunata hu
hai prit jaha ki rit sada

jite ho kisi ne desh to kya, hamne to dilo ko jita hai
jaha ram abhi tak hai nar me, nari me abhi tak sita hai
itne pawan hai log jaha, ho itne pawan hai log jaha
mai nit nit, mai nit nit shish jhukata hu
bharat ka rahne wala hu, bharat kie baat sunata hu

itni mamta nadiyo ko bhi, jaha maata kah ke bulate hai
itna aadar insan to kya, patthar bhi puje jate hai
us dharti pe maine janam liya
ho us dharti pe maine janam liya, ye soch
ye soch ke mai itraata hoo
bharat kaa rahane waala hoo, bharat ki baat sunaata hoo
hai prit jaha ki rit sada
